languages.text: "Нет, это — не мой ритуал!" {n}В мысленный голос хормейстера проникает паника.{/n} "Это его чары! Интервенция в наши разумы! Пока я искал его своей силой, он нашел нас своей! И я... не могу это прекратить! Не могу вышвырнуть его из наших голов!"

"No, this is not my ritual!" {n}Panic rings in the Choirmaster's voice inside your mind.{/n} "This is his spell! An invasion of our minds! While I was seeking it with my power, it found us with its own! And I... cannot stop it! I cannot force it out of our heads!"

languages.text: «¡No, este no es mi ritual!». {n}La voz del Maestro del Coro que resuena en tu cabeza está cargada de pánico.{/n} «¡Este hechizo es suyo! ¡Estaba buscando el mal empleando mi poder, pero nos ha encontrado él! Y... ¡no puedo detenerle! ¡No puedo sacárnoslo de la cabeza!».

languages.text: 「これは私の儀式ではありません！」{n}心の中にクワイアーマスターの慌てふためく声が響く。{/n}「奴の呪文です！我々の心の中へ入り込んでいます！私が己の力で奴を探している間に、奴は己の力で我々を探し出していた！止め…られない！頭から追い出せません！」
languages.original_text: "No, this is not my ritual!" {n}Panic rings in the Choirmaster's voice inside your mind.{/n} "This is his spell! An invasion of our minds! While I was seeking it with my power, it found us with its own! And I... cannot stop it! I cannot force it out of our heads!"

languages.text: “不，仪式已经不受我控制了！”{n}唱诗大师的声音在你的意识中响起，充满了恐慌的意味。{/n}“这是它的恶咒！它在入侵我们的意识！我刚刚试图靠我的力量找到它，可它却抢先找到了我们！我……我停不下来！我没办法把它从我的脑海中赶出去！”
languages.original_text: "No, this is not my ritual!" {n}Panic rings in the Choirmaster's voice inside your mind.{/n} "This is his spell! An invasion of our minds! While I was seeking it with my power, it found us with its own! And I... cannot stop it! I cannot force it out of our heads!"

languages.text: "Nein, das ist nicht mein Ritual!" {n}Die Panik in der Stimme des Chormeisters hallt in deinem Verstand wider.{/n} "Das ist sein Zauber! Eine Invasion unseres Verstandes! Während ich ihn mit meiner Macht suchte, hat er uns gefunden. Und ich ... kann ihn nicht stoppen! Ich kann ihn nicht aus unseren Köpfen verbannen!"
languages.original_text: "No, this is not my ritual!" {n}Panic rings in the Choirmaster's voice inside your mind.{/n} "This is his spell! An invasion of our minds! While I was seeking it with my power, it found us with its own! And I... cannot stop it! I cannot force it out of our heads!"

languages.text: « Non, il ne s'agit pas de mon rituel ! {n}La voix affolée du maître de chœur résonne dans votre esprit.{/n} C'est son sortilège ! Une invasion mentale ! Pendant que je déployais mon pouvoir à sa recherche, c'est lui qui nous a trouvés avec le sien ! Et je... je ne peux rien pour l'arrêter ! Je suis incapable de le chasser de nos pensées ! »
languages.original_text: "No, this is not my ritual!" {n}Panic rings in the Choirmaster's voice inside your mind.{/n} "This is his spell! An invasion of our minds! While I was seeking it with my power, it found us with its own! And I... cannot stop it! I cannot force it out of our heads!"
